**Client:** International Salon Supplies

**Role:** Full Stack Developer

## Features

1. **Restrict Unregistered Users** — limit unregistered users to checkout only for training products; prevent them from viewing or purchasing normal products.
1. **Hide Product Prices** — hide normal product prices for bots and logged-out users; display a "Login to view prices" message.
1. **ERP Integration for Order Management** — automate order placement in the ERP system and reflect real-time order statuses on the website.
1. **Customer Approval Process** — implement a gated customer approval system and automatically notify customers of status changes via email.
1. **Advanced Search with Elasticsearch** — enable full-text search, filters, faceted navigation, auto-suggestions, and typo tolerance.
1. **Abandoned Cart Recovery** — send automated reminders with optional personalised discounts to users who leave carts without purchasing.
1. **Product Recommendations** — display "Frequently Bought Together" sections on product pages.
1. **Customisable Shipping Options** — allow users to choose shipping providers and delivery speeds with real-time cost calculations.
1. **Order Tracking and Notifications** — real-time order tracking on the website and status updates via email or SMS.
1. **Promotions and Discount Management** — create and manage discount codes, flash sales, and promotional campaigns.
1. **Secure Payment Gateway Integration** — integrate PayPal, Tyro, and Afterpay for customer flexibility.
1. **Inventory Management Integration** — sync product inventory between the website and ERP to prevent overselling.
1. **User Account Dashboard** — order history, order tracking, and profile management.
1. **Mobile-First Responsive Design** — fully responsive with touch-friendly navigation and quick product view.
1. **Progressive Web App (PWA)** — add to home screen, native app-like experience, and progressive image loading.

